<h3 id=3D"how-to-use-a-computational-graph">How to use a computational grap=
h ?</h3>
<p>A computational graph is used to represent the computation of a mathemat=
ical function. It is a graph of nodes and edges, where each node represents=
 a mathematical operation and each edge represents the flow of data between=
 the operations.</p>
